      <hedline>
        <hl1>Fuzzy Little Test Tubes</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <abstract>
        <p>David Pogran letter on Lawrence Osborne's July 30 article supports use of lab mice for medical research4</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>Animal rights advocates are not above using emotional arguments, so here's one from a different angle. My wife and best friend for more than half my life died from cancer 14 months ago. If you asked me how many lab rats I'd sacrifice to medical research so that I could have her with me today, the number would be infinite.</p>
        <p>David Pogran  Oakland, Calif.</p>
      </block>
